title: Luxury Residences with Washer/Dryer in unit
posting_body: ['Luxury Residences with Washer/Dryer in unit', 'Listing ID #: 212972', 'Price: $3,300', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 1.0', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Pets: Pets OK', 'Building Amenities', 'Bicycle Room', 'Common Outdoor Space', 'Elevator', 'Garage', 'Laundry', 'New Construction', 'Roof Deck', 'Subway', 'Wheelchair Access', 'WiFi', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood', 'High Ceilings', 'Laundry In Unit', 'Open View', 'Modern one bedroom/one bathroom apartment located in the heart of Astoria, just down the block from Astoria Blvd subway stop.', 'King size bedroom includes your own walk in closet and large windows that bring in lots of natural light.', 'Hardwood floors and high ceilings throughout the apartment.', 'Kitchen comes equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher and modern finishes.', 'Pictures are of a unit with a similar layout and finishes.', 'The building includes a rooftop terrace to enjoy Queens/City views, an indoor gym, and bike storage.', 'Nearby you will find plenty of coffee shops, trending restaurants, grocery stores etc.', 'Contact Sofia to schedule a tour immediately <URL>!', 'Sofia Aguirre', 'Phone: (718) 685-2775', 'Mobile: (718) 424-0813', 'Email: <URL>', 'The Bouklis Group \xa0 (718) 685-2775 \xa0 (718) 424-0813 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Sofia Aguirre at (718) 424-0813']
